data.description: Make your move to the tranquility of Fairfield with this 4 bedroom 3 bathroom ranch home. You will never lack space with over 2700 finished square feet! This well-maintained home is perfect for anyone looking for a relaxing country setting while still being close to all the conveniences that city living has to offer. Situated on 1.84 acres, this house comes with an awesome finished walk-out basement that makes it great for entertaining friends and family.  All this plus newer appliances.  Get ready to fall in love with this beautiful property today!"  Sellers are including a 1 year home warranty!
